<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>42-1306</num>
  <heading>Good faith disclosure.</heading>
  <text>Each disclosure required by this chapter shall be made in good faith. For the purposes of this chapter, “good faith” means honesty in fact in the making of the disclosure.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 12-263" type="History" path="§7">Apr. 20, 1999, D.C. Law 12-263, § 7, 46 DCR 2111</annotation>
